OL,3,C'You're not in control'- MPs grill CEO
OL,4,Cof South East Water over supply outage
OL,6,FThe embattled chief executive of South
OL,7,FEast Water has admitted his company
OL,8,F'did not perform as it should' during
OL,9,Fthe water crisis in Tunbridge Wells,
OL,10,Fwhen he was questioned by MPs on
OL,11,FTuesday (6 December).
OL,13,FDavid Hinton, CEO of South East Water,
OL,14,Fapologised to customers but then
OL,15,Fpointed the finger at "bigger, wider
OL,16,Fquestions here that are not just about
OL,17,FSouth East Water."
