OL,3,C'You're not in control'- MPs grill CEO
OL,4,Cof South East Water over supply outage
OL,6,FThe meeting comes just a couple of
OL,7,Fweeks after thousands of homes were
OL,8,Fleft with no water supply with
OL,9,Fschools, care homes and businesses
OL,10,Fdisrupted in the lead-up to Christmas,
OL,11,Fbecause of an issue at Pembury Water
OL,12,FTreatment Works.
OL,14,FTuesday's meeting, which lasted for
OL,15,Fmore than an hour, led to several
OL,16,Frevelations, including details of a
OL,17,Fphone call between Hinton and Mike
OL,18,FMartin, the local Liberal Democrat MP
OL,19,Ffor Tunbridge Wells.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
