OL,3,C'You're not in control'- MPs grill CEO
OL,4,Cof South East Water over supply outage
OL,6,FIn evidence submitted to the
OL,7,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs
OL,8,FCommittee, Martin said that Hinton
OL,9,Faccused him of 'politicising' the
OL,10,Fwater crisis as it was unfolding.
OL,12,FMartin's evidence said: "(Hinton)
OL,13,Fasked me how I could sleep at night
OL,14,Fhaving 'politicised' the issue."
OL,16,FIn response, Hinton told the
OL,17,Fcommittee, "It wasn't my finest moment.
OL,19,F"The things Mike said to me elicited
OL,20,Fthat kind of response and the rest of
OL,21,Fit was a private conversation."
