OL,3,C'You're not in control'- MPs grill CEO
OL,4,Cof South East Water over supply outage
OL,6,FDuring the meeting, Alistair
OL,7,FCarmichael, committee chair and
OL,8,FLiberal Democrat MP for Orkney and
OL,9,FShetland, quizzed the chief executive
OL,10,Fon his handling of the outage which
OL,11,Faffected more than 24,000 homes.
OL,13,FAsked to score his response to the
OL,14,Fcrisis out of 10, Hinton said: "I'd
OL,15,Fgive you three numbers. Eight out of
OL,16,Ften in terms of response, six out of
OL,17,Ften in terms of communications, and
OL,18,Fsix out of ten in terms of the actual
OL,19,Fprevention of the event in the first
OL,20,Fplace."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
