OL,3,C'You're not in control'- MPs grill CEO
OL,4,Cof South East Water over supply outage
OL,6,FCarmichael then accused the chief
OL,7,Fexecutive of not having control of his
OL,8,Fcompany. "It doesn't sound to me like
OL,9,Fa company that as a community-based
OL,10,Fcompany is taking responsibility for
OL,11,Fits own actions," he said.
OL,13,F"It sounds like you're not really in
OL,14,Fcontrol of your own business."
OL,16,FExplaining the reasons for the outage,
OL,17,FHinton said it was the result of "an
OL,18,Funexpected failure" of the chemicals
OL,19,Fwhich are used to treat the water for
OL,20,FTunbridge Wells.
