OL,3,C'You're not in control'- MPs grill CEO
OL,4,Cof South East Water over supply outage
OL,6,FHe added that changes to the make-up
OL,7,Fof the spring water the local plant
OL,8,Fuses, were possibly the result of
OL,9,Fclimate change.
OL,11,F"The South-East of England is
OL,12,Fparticularly hit with climate change
OL,13,Fimpacts," he said, adding "We've had
OL,14,Fcontinual growth in housing forever
OL,15,Fand this has meant demand has got very
OL,16,Fclose to our ability to supply."
