OL,3,C'You're not in control'- MPs grill CEO
OL,4,Cof South East Water over supply outage
OL,6,F"We've shored up a number of areas
OL,7,Fwhere resilience was challenged in
OL,8,Fthese heat waves, areas in Sussex and
OL,9,Fother areas in Kent. We've got a plan
OL,10,Fto shore up Tunbridge Wells."
OL,12,FIn total, tens of thousands of people
OL,13,Flost their water supply with schools,
OL,14,Fcare homes and businesses disrupted in
OL,15,Fthe lead-up to Christmas.
