OL,3,C'You're not in control'- MPs grill CEO
OL,4,Cof South East Water over supply outage
OL,6,FIt took nine days for South East Water
OL,7,Fto restore running water to the whole
OL,8,Farea after the issue at Pembury
OL,9,Ftreatment works. Normal services only
OL,10,Fresumed when a 'boil notice' was
OL,11,Flifted two weeks after the outage
OL,12,Fbegan.
OL,14,FAs chief executive of the company,
OL,15,FHinton refused to appear in public or
OL,16,Fspeak to the media throughout the
OL,17,Fcrisis.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
