OL,3,C'You're not in control'- MPs grill CEO
OL,4,Cof South East Water over supply outage
OL,6,FIt was only 20 days after the outage
OL,7,Fstarted that he gave his first
OL,8,Finterview where he told ITV Meridian
OL,9,Fhe would not resign. Last year,
OL,10,FHinton's base salary was increased by
OL,11,Fmore than 30% to #400,000.
OL,13,FBusinesses affected by the outage are
OL,14,Fstill measuring the costs of lost
OL,15,Frevenue, however.
