OL,3,C'You're not in control'- MPs grill CEO
OL,4,Cof South East Water over supply outage
OL,6,FHinton opened today's meeting with an
OL,7,Fapology to people affected in
OL,8,FTunbridge Wells, a number of whom have
OL,9,Falready been compensated for the
OL,10,Foutage. Small businesses are expected
OL,11,Fto receive compensation in the region
OL,12,Fof three or four times their annual
OL,13,Fwater bill.
OL,15,FHinton said: "My ultimate
OL,16,Faccountability is absolutely to the
OL,17,Fcustomer. particularly in terms of
OL,18,Fwater quality but water supply as
OL,19,Fwell. they are the two top areas of
OL,20,Ffocus.
